### Get team for organization [GET]

#### Permissions requirements
* Super admin
* Role for this organization

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {"teams":[{"members":[{"user":{"id":1,"first_name":"Hampus","last_name":"Iggstr\u00f6m"}}],"id":2,"name":"Salesmans"}]}


### Create team for organization [POST]

#### Permissions requirements
* Super admin
* Role for this organization

