## Profile picture [/organizations/{organization_id}/teams/{id}/pictures]

+ Parameters

    + organization_id: `34` (required, number) - The organization ID.
    + id: `41` (required, number) - The team ID.

#### Upload profile picture [POST]

Upload a new profile picture for a team. The picture will be cropped in a square. Supported file format is png, jpeg.

#### Permissions requirements
* Super admin
* Organization admin

+ Request (multipart/form-data; charset=utf-8; boundary=CONTENT)

    + Body

            --CONTENT
            Content-Disposition: form-data; name="upload[file]"; filename="name.png"
            Content-Type: image/png

            PNG

            ..PNG-body..


+ Response 201 (application/json)

    + Body

            {"team":{"members":[{"user":{"registration_completed":true,"id":1,"email":"hampus@spire.se","first_name":"Hampus","last_name":"Iggstr\u00f6m","profile_picture":{"url":"http:\/\/api.pushappy.com\/media\/cache\/profile_picture\/uploads\/images\/dd39c216bc8326fbe9fe81b0979f32aaea589d48.jpeg"}}}],"id":2,"name":"Smedjan","profile_picture":{"url":"http:\/\/api.pushappy.com\/media\/cache\/profile_picture\/uploads\/images\/5ca504b3c0be4ebaa6c40ef59a1ba4a67536a18a.png"}}}

#### Remove profile picture [DELETE]

Removes the current profile picture from the given team.

#### Permissions requirements
* Super admin
* Organization admin

+ Request (application/json)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

    + Body

            {"team":{"members":[{"user":{"registration_completed":true,"id":1,"email":"hampus@spire.se","first_name":"Hampus","last_name":"Iggstr\u00f6m","profile_picture":{"url":"http:\/\/api.pushappy.com\/media\/cache\/profile_picture\/uploads\/images\/dd39c216bc8326fbe9fe81b0979f32aaea589d48.jpeg"}}}],"id":2,"name":"Smedjan"}}

